summary:
“Who cares?” Brie Larson asked about fans that don’t like Captain Marvel.
Meanwhile, I was getting upset about it all effing...
body:
“Who cares?” Brie Larson asked about fans that don’t like Captain Marvel.

Meanwhile, I was getting upset about it all effing weekend. Like if you guys can’t handle, blonde, beautiful Carol simply not smiling in the poster then how can we have a Kamala movie?

summary: Heading to the Captain Marvel Red Carpet Premiere today!
title: Heading to the Captain Marvel Red Carpet Premiere today!
body:
I’m going as Mina’s plus one, and she’ll be in her amazing new Carol suit, but it’s a lot of costume, so I’m going to be assisting/taking photos, so I’m just going in casual Peter Parker!

I’ll post photos and my thoughts on the film tomorrow, but if you want to follow the adventure, I’ll be posting on my story! Check out my Instagram at @aaronrivin
